                    </p>
                    <br><br>
                    <h3 class="qAndA">What Can I Do In Pinkish Vibes ?</h3>
                    <p class="articleText">
                        You can add, delete and edit any article. You also can (heart) your favourite articles so you can view them in the favourite articles page.
                    </p>
                    <br><br>
                    <h3 class="qAndA">Are There any Rules On Posting Articles ?</h3>
                    <p class="articleText">
                        No,there isn't. as long as you're posting an appropriate, beneficial articles in the right category, you're free to post whatever you like
                    </p>
                    <br><br>
                    <h3 class="qAndA">Any Additional Notes ?</h3>
                    <p class="articleText">
                        If you are a user please support us and let us know about your opinions and suggestions about this blog in the feedbacks page.               and if you have admin's password you'll be able to access admin's control panel and view the statistics and feedbacks.
